      "span_text": "Several other nuclear proteins were also recently identified to be involved in NF-κB signaling regulation in the nucleus, such as the protein kinase A-interacting protein 1 (AKIP1) [CITATION_1] and the CHFR protein, encoded by checkpoint with forkhead and ring finger domains gene [CITATION_2] (Table 1) ."
